{"tid":1026829,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国人團體擬設「大阪中華街」 地區團體憂滋擾","createTime":"2019-02-18T11:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T12:07:11.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c228f4479ed38c3825cae43a5f309160e5033a81","tid":1026829,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:26:13.000Z","msg":"日本大阪一個由當地中國人組成的團體，正計劃推動在市內西成區建設「大阪中華街」，望能成為新的觀光景點。不過有地區團體就認為計劃太突然。<br />\n<br />\n由大阪的中國籍房地產相關人士等組成的團體「大阪華商會」，今日召開會議，計劃爭取在2025年大阪世博會前，在西成區的商店街開設共約100間中餐館、雜貨店、文化設施等。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐大阪總領事李天然等約200人出席會議，李天然表示，在市內西成區建設「大阪中華街」，能令西成區成為新景點。另外，有在構想區域內的店主亦指，相信該構想能為當區帶來活力。然而，飛田本通商店街振興協會理事長村井康夫則指，擔心會導致垃圾及噪音問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1434573/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1434573%2F&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgKwvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=d9904f0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1434573%2F&h=78e9b26c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1434573/</a>"},{"pid":"9cc2e53bfdf3020d30eff41074b379303a96c555","tid":1026829,"uid":137804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:33:04.000Z","msg":"隔離新地 唔好亂搞呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227bc80965eb58bc07243afa86235413103ad3c0","tid":1026829,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:34:29.000Z","msg":"西成區都想吞埋人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62b8c11f6c3907749f5f664d705cf2974708424","tid":1026829,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:36:51.000Z","msg":"大阪唐人街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281a9477fbd33b4a6550766c2877abbd77c8fe00","tid":1026829,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"